title: Hour 2 - Receiver Caused Interceptions, CFP Week 2
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Receiver Caused Interceptions, CFP Week 2
description:
After watching last night's performance from Los Angeles Rams QB Matt Stafford, Dan spends some time discussing RCI (receiver caused interception). And he previews the most interesting matchups for week 2 of the college football season.
